(Worked Examples) Tj
T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on comparing sodium chloride and water bonding.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in why atoms bond and what each bond type looks like that the) Tj
T*
(question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Chemical Bonding step by step without skipping) Tj
T*
(reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
